## Summary
This document explains Monthly Tracking Users (MTU) billing in Amplitude, detailing how MTUs are calculated (unique users triggering events within a calendar month), usage limits across different plans (up to 1M MTUs for Growth/Enterprise), and how to monitor MTU consumption. It addresses common scenarios affecting MTU counts like anonymous users, cross-project tracking, and data backfills.

